00:06:01.461 --> 00:06:06.439
you to complete these surveys for
like a dollar a person, right?

107
00:06:06.439 --> 00:06:09.370
It's so easy,
there is no reason not to do this.

108
00:06:09.370 --> 00:06:14.972
You think how many man hours have been
wasted sitting in meetings, debating

